title: rustdoc compilation error for aarch64-linux-android
body:
the compilation of rustdoc crate for target `aarch64-linux-android` failed to compile.

it seems the `os` module in crate isn't defined for `target_os="android"`. But as I don't have this platform, I can't check how implement it.
